lead_paragraph: Hillary Rodham Clinton, making her return to Iowa for the first time since the 2008 presidential campaign, implored Democrats on Sunday to choose shared economic opportunity over "the guardians of gridlock" in an high-profile appearance that drove speculation about another White House bid into overdrive.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton in Iowa Stirs 2016 Speculation
headline.print_headline: Hillary Clinton in Iowa Stirs 2016 Speculation
